title: Middletown field hockey makes best of chances in win
text: Middletown field hockey makes best of chances in win KEVIN PHILLIPS, SPECIAL TO THE NEWS JOURNAL 8:50 p.m. EDT October 7, 2015 Buy Photo Mount Pleasant's Tionne Henson (right) works the ball past Middletown's Sara Feldmann (left) in the first half of Middletown's 4-2 win over Mount Pleasant at Middletown High School on Wednesday afternoon. KYLE GRANTHAM/THE NEWS JOURNAL Fullscreen Buy Photo Mount Pleasant Kate Walker (left) moves the ball past Middletown's Sara Feldmann (right) in the first half of Middletown's 4-2 win over Mount Pleasant at Middletown High School on Wednesday afternoon.
